definition.value: Catalysis of the transfer of an alpha-D-glucosyl residue from sucrose to alternately the 6-position and the 3-position of the non-reducing terminal residue of an alpha-D-glucan, thus producing a glucan having alternating alpha-1,6- and alpha-1,3-linkages.

Catalysis of the transfer of the non-reducing terminal alpha-D-glucose residue from a 1,4-alpha-D-glucan to the 4-position of an alpha-D-glucan, thus bringing about the hydrolysis of oligosaccharides.
Catalysis of the transfer of a beta-D-glucosyl residue from UDP-glucose on to a glucose residue in xyloglucan, forming a beta-1,4-D-glucosyl-D-glucose linkage.

Catalysis of the transfer of an N-acetyl-D-glucosamine residue from UDP-N-acetyl-D-glucosamine to the 4-position of a mannose linked alpha-1,6 to the core mannose of high-mannose oligosaccharides produced by Dictyostelium discoideum.
Catalysis of the reaction -  sn-glycerol 3-phosphate + ADP-glucose -eq- 2-O-(beta-D-glucosyl)-sn-glycerol 3-phosphate + ADP + H(+).
Catalysis of the transfer of a beta-D-GlcNAc residue from UDP-D-GlcNAc to the fucose residue of a fucosylated protein acceptor.
Catalysis of the reaction -  UDP-N-acetylglucosamine + Skp1-protein-hydroxyproline -eq- UDP + Skp1-protein-O-(N-acetyl-D-glucosaminyl)hydroxyproline.
Catalysis of the reaction -  kojibiose + phosphate -eq- beta-D-glucose 1-phosphate + D-glucose.
Catalysis of the reaction -  alpha,alpha-trehalose + phosphate -eq- alpha-D-glucose + alpha-D-glucose 1-phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  5-hydroxymethylfurfural + NADH + H+ -eq- 2,5-bis-hydroxymethylfuran + NAD+.
Catalysis of the reaction -  UDP-galactose + kaempferol -eq- UDP + kaempferol 3-O-beta-D-galactoside.
Catalysis of the reaction -  UDP-L-rhamnose + a flavanone 7-O-glucoside -eq- UDP + a flavanone 7-O-[beta-L-rhamnosyl-(1--gt-2)-beta-D-glucoside].
Catalysis of the reaction -  UDP-glucose + a flavonol -eq- UDP + a flavonol 7-O-beta-D-glucoside.
Catalysis of the reaction -  UDP-glucose + an anthocyanin -eq- UDP + an anthocyanin 3'-O-beta-D-glucoside.
Catalysis of the reaction -  UDP-glucose + a flavonol 3-O-beta-D-glucoside -eq- UDP + a flavonol 3-O-beta-D-glucosyl-(1--gt-2)-beta-D-glucoside.
Catalysis of the reaction -  UDP-glucose + a flavonol 3-O-beta-D-glucosyl-(1--gt-2)-beta-D-glucoside -eq- UDP + a flavonol 3-O-beta-D-glucosyl-(1--gt-2)-beta-D-glucosyl-(1--gt-2)-beta-D-glucoside.
Catalysis of the reaction -  NDP-glucose + (1,4-alpha-D-glucosyl)n -eq- NDP + (1,4-alpha-D-glucosyl)n+1.

Catalysis of the reaction -  [1-beta-D-fructofuranosyl-(2--gt-1)-]m+1 alpha-D-glucopyranoside + [1-beta-D-fructofuranosyl-(2--gt-1)-]n+1 alpha-D-glucopyranoside -eq- [1-beta-D-fructofuranosyl-(2--gt-1)-]m alpha-D-glucopyranoside + [1-beta-D-fructofuranosyl-(2--gt-1)-]n+1 beta-D-fructofuranosyl-(2--gt-6)-alpha-D-glucopyranoside (m -gt- 0 -  n -gt--eq- 0).
Catalysis of the reaction -  UDP-N-acetyl-D-galactosamine + N-acetyl-beta-D-glucosaminyl group -eq- UDP + N-acetyl-beta-D-galactosaminyl-(1--gt-4)-N-acetyl-beta-D-glucosaminyl group.
Catalysis of the transfer of an alpha-D-xylosyl residue from UDP-D-xylose to a glucose residue in xyloglucan, forming an alpha-1,6-D-xylosyl-D-glucose linkage.
Catalysis of the elimination of sulfate from the D-galactose 6-sulfate residues of porphyran, producing 3,6-anhydrogalactose residues.
Catalysis of the reaction -  5-hydroxymethylfurfural + NADPH + H+ -eq- 2,5-bis-hydroxymethylfuran + NADP+.
Catalysis of the reaction -  S-adenosyl-L-methionine + fluoride -eq- 5'-deoxy-5'-fluoroadenosine + L-methionine.
Catalysis of the reaction -  O-phospho-L-serine + hydrogen sulfide -eq- L-cysteine + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  D-glyceraldehyde 3-phosphate + L-arginine -eq- N(2)-(2-carboxyethyl)-L-arginine + H(+) + phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2 dimethylallyl diphosphate -eq- (R,R)-chrysanthemyl diphosphate + diphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  geranyl diphosphate + isopentenyl diphosphate -eq- 2-cis,6-trans-farnesyl diphosphate + diphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2 dimethylallyl diphosphate -eq- diphosphate + lavandulyl diphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-oxoglutarate + 3,5,3'-triiodo-L-thyronine -eq- 3,5,3'-triiodothyropyruvate + L-glutamate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  L-arogenate + oxaloacetate -eq- prephenate + L-aspartate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-oxoglutarate + L-arogenate -eq- L-glutamate + prephenate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  2-oxoglutarate + nicotianamine -eq- 3''-deamino-3''-oxonicotianamine + L-glutamate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  1-deoxy-D-xylulose 5-phosphate + 3-amino-2-oxopropyl phosphate -eq- 2 H(2)O + H(+) + phosphate + pyridoxine 5'-phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + 1D-myo-inositol 5-diphosphate pentakisphosphate -eq- ADP + 1D-myo-inositol bisdiphosphate tetrakisphosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + N-acetyl-D-galactosamine -eq- ADP + N-acetyl-alpha-D-galactosamine 1-phosphate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + UMP -eq- ADP + UDP.
Catalysis of the reaction -  D-ribose 1,5-diphosphate + ATP -eq- 5-phospho-alpha-D-ribose 1-diphosphate + ADP + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + Fas-activated serine|threonine protein -eq- ADP + Fas-activated serine|threonine phosphoprotein.
Catalysis of the reaction -  ATP + Goodpasture antigen-binding protein -eq- ADP + Goodpasture antigen-binding phosphoprotein.
Catalysis of the reaction -  3'-phosphoadenylyl sulfate + a thiol -eq- adenosine 3',5'-bisphosphate + an S-alkyl thiosulfate.

Catalysis of the reaction -  3'-phosphoadenylyl sulfate + [heparan sulfate]-glucosamine -eq- adenosine 3',5'-bisphosphate + [heparan sulfate]-glucosamine 3-sulfate -  modifies selected glucosamine residues preceded by GlcA2S.
Catalysis of the reaction -  3'-phosphoadenylyl sulfate + [heparan sulfate]-glucosamine -eq- adenosine 3',5'-bisphosphate + [heparan sulfate]-glucosamine 3-sulfate.

Catalysis of the reaction -  3'-phospho-5'-adenylyl sulfate + 5alpha-cholane-3alpha,7alpha,12alpha,24-tetrol -eq- 3alpha,7alpha,12alpha-trihydroxy-5alpha-cholan-24-yl sulfate + adenosine 3',5'-diphosphate + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  3'-phospho-5'-adenylyl sulfate + 5beta-scymnol -eq- 5beta-scymnol sulfate + adenosine 3',5'-diphosphate + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  3'-phospho-5'-adenylyl sulfate + glycochenodeoxycholate -eq- adenosine 3',5'-diphosphate + glycochenodeoxycholate 7-sulfate + H(+).
Catalysis of the reaction -  (R)-2-benzylsuccinate + succinyl-CoA -eq- (R)-2-benzylsuccinyl-CoA + succinate.

Catalysis of the reactions -  diacylglycerol + H2O -eq- monoacylglycerol + a carboxylate -  triacylglycerol + H2O -eq- diacylglycerol + a carboxylate -  and monoacylglycerol + H2O -eq- glycerol + a carboxylate.
Catalysis of the reactions -  17-O-acetylajmaline + H2O -eq- ajmaline + acetate, and 17-O-acetylnorajmaline + H2O -eq- norajmaline + acetate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  H(2)O + phenylglyoxylyl-CoA -eq- CoA + H(+) + phenylglyoxylate.
Catalysis of the reaction -  deoxycholoyl-CoA + H(2)O -eq- CoA + deoxycholate + H(+).
